OL,3,CSupermarket staff taught to use bleed
OL,4,Ckits after fatal stabbings in city
OL,6,FA supermarket has brought staff
OL,7,Ftogether in Bristol for bleed kit
OL,8,Ftraining.
OL,10,FSince Christmas, four teenagers have
OL,11,Fdied after being stabbed in the city,
OL,12,Fprompting calls for more to be done to
OL,13,Fkeep young people safe.
OL,15,FThis has triggered a large roll-out of
OL,16,Fequipment across the city - primarily
OL,17,Fbleed kits.
