OL,3,CSupermarket staff taught to use bleed
OL,4,Ckits after fatal stabbings in city
OL,6,FLeanne Reynolds, a knife crime
OL,7,Fcampaigner, said: "It started in 2021
OL,8,Fafter I worked with two young men who
OL,9,Flost their lives due to serious
OL,10,Fviolence in the city.
OL,12,F"Ever since I've wanted to find a
OL,13,Fpreventative measure, so I found bleed
OL,14,Fkits and I launched them. It could
OL,15,Fpotentially save a life while they're
OL,16,Fwaiting for emergency services."
OL,18,FAsda staff from stores across Bristol
OL,19,Fcame together for the training on
OL,20,FTuesday 21 May.
