OL,6,FGrant Lewis was the one to train them.
OL,7,FHe said: "All over the country they've
OL,8,Fbeen used and successfully saved
OL,9,Flives."
OL,11,FIn just the last few months, hundreds
OL,12,Fof kits have been distributed across
OL,13,FBristol. And while the scheme was
OL,14,Fstarted with crime in mind, it has
OL,15,Fother benefits.
OL,17,FBrenda, a community champion who
OL,18,Fhelped organise the training, said:
OL,19,F"It's not necessarily to do with knife
OL,20,Fcrime, it could be any catastrophic
OL,21,Fbleed.
